Package: spatialwidget
Type: Package
Title: Converts Spatial Data for use in Htmlwidgets
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-10-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Cooley", ,"dcooley@symbolix.com.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Many packages use 'htmlwidgets' for interactive plotting of spatial data.
    This package provides functions for converting R objects, such as simple features, 
    into structures suitable for use in 'htmlwidgets'. 
